{"tid":1022786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】大陸官方推出「學習強國」App","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T14:02:31.000Z","uid":89543,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"20384b0007053e4db6d278be85367236103d7b7e","tid":1022786,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"中國官方宣傳國家主席習近平個人形象不遺餘力，近來配合高度發展的智慧型手機科技，推出一款名為「學習強國」的習語錄APP，官方強迫近9千萬黨員下載使用，並透過積分制變相強迫黨員每天使用，成效較低者還會被通報檢討，已引發內部反彈。<br />\n<br />\n「學習強國」由中國中央宣傳部推出，被稱為是線上版小紅書、習語錄，自2月1日推出後，高居蘋果App商店排行榜首；中國在今年19屆二中全會後，通過將「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」寫入中國《憲法》。<br />\n<br />\n「學習強國」內容除了習近平最新報導外，還能溫習習近平思想，觀看電視節目《習近平時間》，並參加測驗賺取積分，未來可憑積分兌換獎品。中國媒體形容，「學習強國」獲全國民眾熱烈反響，甚至有長輩為此省吃儉用購入智慧型手機，但也傳出有人因積分不足被通報檢討。"},{"pid":"e1f9cd461207eba9506bcf36198a712bc8f33431","tid":1022786,"uid":177779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"752cf770e2809c0588bdd36cd2be14f6b63bf546","tid":1022786,"uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"網頁版：<a href=\"https://www.xuexi.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xuexi.cn%2F&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=f2f687f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xuexi.cn/</a>"},{"pid":"9f5823323a036608fbac35c2f8892ad154efe842","tid":1022786,"uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"手機下載：<a href=\"http://app.mi.com/details?id=cn.xuexi.android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp.mi.com%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcn.xuexi.android&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=88a10f88\" target=\"_blank\">http://app.mi.com/details?id=cn.xuexi.android</a>"},{"pid":"bd65e26fc8eee229bcb2283ccabf1c3798d69ff3","tid":1022786,"uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"仲有答題遊戲玩，好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hk